e-to-back-injury-3817517">最近因背部受伤取消了在俄克拉荷马城的演出。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queens-of-the-stone-age-bicep-justin-timberlake-lead-electric-castle-2025-line-up-in-transylvania-3821357">石器时代女王、Bicep 和 Justin Timberlake 领衔特兰西瓦尼亚 2025 年电动城堡阵容</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
